title: Dave Matthews Band - Live Trax 2008
description:
1. Eh Hee - 6.24.08 (Mansfield)
2. So Damn Lucky - 6.28.08 (Nissan)
3. Crush - 6.10.08 (Scranton)
4. The Dreaming Tree - 6.21.08 (SPAC)
5. Pay for What You Get - 6.10.08 (Scranton)
6. Proudest Monkey - 6.24.08 (Mansfield)
7. Bartender - 8.19.08 (Los Angeles)
8. Tripping Billies - 8.10.08 (Alpine) 

This CD is avaible for FREE download for those who bought ticket at ticketmaster.org 

Included 8 tracks in mp3/256kbps

Hope You enjoy this relase, it included So Damn Lucky with extended outro and emotional Bartender (which was the first song played after Roi's death).

(First 6 songs are with Roi, songs 7 and 8 are with Jeff Cofflin)
